{"author":{"id":"73b707dd3f6d0c02a3a4f870bb84d4c00150b72b88aff75826f08696971dde18"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1673454952,"nonce":"c1Gy3Nt78QyC66Rpw4DJ1CjWdqc=","metadata":{"github-id":"IC_kwDOAW4Y0s5SM5Ph","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/5046#issuecomment-1379111905"},"message":"Maybe it's a mere misconception regarding the content of `database_path/amrfinderplus-db`. AMRfinderplus puts date schema-named subfolders for each database version into its database path, *along* with a `latest` link pointing to the latest db version. Bakta expects this `latest` link within the `database_path/amrfinderplus-db` dir. I hope this is helpful.\n\n```\n$ ls -l databases/bakta/db-v4.0/amrfinderplus-db/\ndrwxrwxr-x 2 oliver oliver 4,0K Aug 26 10:37 2022-08-09.1/\nlrwxrwxrwx 1 oliver oliver   70 Sep 27 09:21 latest -\u003e /home/foo/databases/bakta/db-v4.0/amrfinderplus-db/2022-08-09.1/\n```","files":null},{"type":6,"timestamp":1673455037,"nonce":"4o96ubHV2Ti07i+FxuOtrLALQI4=","metadata":{"github-id":"UCE_lALOAW4Y0s5SM5PhziuQYjE"},"target":"162f1e98b8b332903c801adfb37ddaa72996a1f12cb0119437adedf1f5cd0fd5","message":"Maybe it's a mere misconception regarding the content of `database_path/amrfinderplus-db`. AMRfinderplus puts date schema-named subfolders for each database version into its database path, *along* with a `latest` link pointing to the latest db version. Bakta expects this `latest` link within the `database_path/amrfinderplus-db` dir. I hope this is helpful.\n\nExample:\n```\n$ ls -l databases/bakta/db-v4.0/amrfinderplus-db/\ndrwxrwxr-x 2 oliver oliver 4,0K Aug 26 10:37 2022-08-09.1/\nlrwxrwxrwx 1 oliver oliver   70 Sep 27 09:21 latest -\u003e /home/foo/databases/bakta/db-v4.0/amrfinderplus-db/2022-08-09.1/\n```","files":null}]}